title: Above & Beyond - Acoustic USA - The Greek Theatre - October
description:
Following the success of their recent run of acoustic shows at London's Porchester Hall, Above & Beyond will bring their acoustic project to the US for a special one night event in Los Angeles on October 12!

Presenting some of their best-loved songs in acoustic form, the show will be hosted at a legendary LA venue (to be revealed soon) and represents the first stateside 'unplugged' show in the band's 13-year history.

Enjoy Trance Family!
